@startuml fig-arp-protocol
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title Flux Protocol ARP

participant "Host A\n192.168.1.10\nAA:AA" as A
participant "Switch" as S
participant "Host B\n192.168.1.20\nBB:BB" as B

A -> S : ARP Request (broadcast)\nCine are 192.168.1.20?
S -> B : Broadcast
B -> S : ARP Reply (unicast)\n192.168.1.20 este la BB:BB
S -> A : Forward

A -> B : Pachet IP cu MAC corect

legend right
ARP Request: dest ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
ARP Reply: unicast catre solicitant
Cache: arp -a, ip neigh show
Captura: tcpdump arp
endlegend
@enduml
